title: Title: Core DAO nomination for Blight Night @BlightNight
body:
TG Discussion Link : https://t.me/acryptos9/12549

Description: 
Blight Night is involved in ACryptoS project for over a month now, and he has been helping the project as a community member.
Often act in interest of the acsACS holders, he would be a fit for the Core DAO Team in order to help the project move forward. 
Things he excel in :
- Help with the management of the TG channels
- Offer ideas to move the project forward (tokenomics/PR/administration)
- Assist the community (especially newcomers)
- Organization of various documentations
